casebody.data:
STALDER
v.
BUCHER 2019-0574 Supreme Court of Ohio. July 10, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

APPEALS NOT ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW

Intervening appellee's "motion to vacate lower courts' void judgments, or, alternatively, for leave to intervene" denied.

Kennedy, J., concurs in part and dissents in part and would grant the motion to vacate and deny the request to accept jurisdiction as moot.
